title: SPELL Partnered Stake Pool and Farm
body:
**SpookySwap Welcomes SPELL Community to Partnered Staking!**
xBOO holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you the next partnered staking pool featuring SPELL.

**The xBOO Pool:**
Stake xBOO tokens to earn SPELL tokens!
* Total Tokens: 4,500,000 SPELL
* Distribution duration: 60 days
* Start time: 1634054400 October 12th, 2021 1600 UTC
* Finish time: 1639238400 December 11th, 2021 1600 UTC
* Token rewards per second: 0.868055 SPELL


**The Farm:**
In addition to the SPELL xBOO Pool, we would provide a SPELL-FTM farm that will have 2x BOO rewards for the first 48 hours and then 1x BOO rewards after that.

**What is SPELL?**
Abracadabra is a magical protocol to make your crypto work for you. You can assets as collateral to mint Magic Internet Money (MIM). Due to the fact that MIM is backed by ibTKNs, your collateral value is always increasing. So what is MIM you may ask? MIM is a USD pegged stable coin. As with most stablecoins, it is traded on markets with other stablecoins such as USDT, DAI, and USDC. SPELL can be staked in the protocol to get sSPELL which earns protocol fees.


**To learn more about SPELL Community, Grim advises you to visit their official communication channels:**
* Website: https://abracadabra.money/
* Twitter: https://twitter.com/MIM_Spell
* Blog: https://medium.com/abracadabra-money
* Discord: https://discord.com/invite/wcsUNxYrFM
* CoinGecko: https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/spell-token


**How do you stake xBOO to earn SPELL rewards?**
If you own BOO tokens, congratulations! You’re one step away from staking xBOO. It’s easy to learn how to stake xBOO for Partnered Staking.
* Visit this webpage: https://spookyswap.finance/pools
* Click “Approve” on the Buyback BOO Single Stake pool
* Click on the “+ Stake” button
* Enter your amount of BOO
* Confirm the transaction, this will get you xBOO
* Then, click “Approve” on the SPELL Pool
* Click on the “+ Stake” button
* Enter your amount of xBOO
* Confirm the transaction


**SPELL Address**

Beware scam tokens! The correct SPELL address is: 0x468003B688943977e6130F4F68F23aad939a1040
